    <p class="mb-4">
      Healthcare in Cayman is good quality but expensive. The main hospital is in George Town, with clinics throughout Grand Cayman. Complex cases often go to Miami.
    </p>

    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-3">Healthcare Facilities</h3>

    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 mb-6">
      <li><strong>Health City Cayman Islands</strong> - Modern, JCI-accredited, comprehensive services</li>
      <li><strong>Cayman Islands Hospital</strong> - George Town, public hospital</li>
      <li><strong>Doctors Hospital</strong> - Private care, various specialists</li>
      <li><strong>Various private clinics</strong> - GP and specialist services</li>
    </ul>

    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-3">Sample Costs (Without Insurance)</h3>

    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
