      <li><strong>Emergency room:</strong> $500-1,500</li>
      <li><strong>Hospital stay:</strong> $1,500-3,000+/day</li>
      <li><strong>Medical evacuation to Miami:</strong> $10,000-30,000</li>
    </ul>

